## Template Variables
## $item:			Item object of class ca.ualberta.library.ir.model.solr.Item.
## $url:			Task in the Pool URL.
## $viewItemUrl:	Item handle URL.
## $user:			User object contains fields: firstName, lastName, email.
## $admin:			Admin email address.

Welcome to ERA: Education and Research Archive.

A new item has been submitted:

Title:        $item.titles.get(0)
Community:    #foreach ($community in $item.communities)#if($velocityCount>1), #end$community.title#end

#if($item.collections.size()>0)
Collection:   #foreach ($collection in $item.collections)#if($velocityCount>1), #end$collection.title#end
#end

#if($item.thesisDegreeDisciplines.size()>0)
Department:   #foreach ($department in $item.thesisDegreeDisciplines)#if($velocityCount>1), #end$department#end
#end

URL:          $viewItemUrl
Submitted by: $user.firstName $user.lastName ($user.email)

The submission must be checked before inclusion in the archive.

To claim this task, please visit your "myERA" page:  $url
